{"tid":2026544,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"攬炒藝術家 ：政府「兇」岑敖暉之突破盲腸：變相承認黑警殺人？","createTime":"2020-05-21T04:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T05:41:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a639d164f65576478e525a29fcc0509440cd38dd","tid":2026544,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:31:07.000Z","msg":"律政司發信要求岑敖暉七天內移除文章〈周梓樂被香港警察謀殺身亡，半年〉，否則或涉「促進、鼓勵或煸動暴力」。氣憤以言入罪之餘，要突破盲腸：為什麼不告誹謗？<br />\n<br />\n誹謗罪要求由原告（而非被告）證明並非事實，被告則可用公允評論、真誠相信作抗辯。政府喜歡說這類說話：你投訴、告我囉，唔敢就即係心虛啦。用政府的邏輯，政府不敢告誹謗，意味政府變相承認黑警殺人乃事實？尤其監警會不是已公佈了所謂「真相」？反正政府已經控告了不少抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉決定不刪除該文，並且揭露政府的威嚇。支持你的決定，抗衡以言入罪，並為政府的醜惡留下紀錄。林鄭說要打擊網上謠言，敢不敢告誹謗？我倒想看看政府拿出證據，證明沒有黑警殺人。以後政府指控什麼謠言，先反問一句：敢告誹謗嗎？難怪林鄭說要認真研究如何監察網上假消息 （俗稱「網禁」），也許要加什麼法例方便「莫須有」，不用像誹謗罪要原告證明「並非事實」才告得入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%85%87-%E5%B2%91%E6%95%96%E6%9A%89%E4%B9%8B%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E7%9B%B2%E8%85%B8-%E8%AE%8A%E7%9B%B8%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E5%2585%2587-%25E5%25B2%2591%25E6%2595%2596%25E6%259A%2589%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E7%259B%25B2%25E8%2585%25B8-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=9d16dc94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E5%2585%2587-%25E5%25B2%2591%25E6%2595%2596%25E6%259A%2589%25E4%25B9%258B%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E7%259B%25B2%25E8%2585%25B8-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=30e28145\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%85%87-%E5%B2%91%E6%95%96%E6%9A%89%E4%B9%8B%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E7%9B%B2%E8%85%B8-%E8%AE%8A%E7%9B%B8%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA/</a>"},{"pid":"77732cb3a32d339b6a273d2d16929b2481782b14","tid":2026544,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"lm睇告<br />\n<br />\n定駱大總統未落指示？"},{"pid":"c84bbe8dbb4ccdad96ec55de97b920f7731f6c67","tid":2026544,"uid":119188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b08db23a17fc9866ce119ee079b24fddb4d15e","tid":2026544,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:15:47.000Z","msg":"可惜紅官唔係咁睇<br />\nRIP"},{"pid":"e6aa1a1c1a764072a81925cdf553c08d4983079e","tid":2026544,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:35:06.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba94ca8d330dd4dd31bc974fff7c998eaa11c8e","tid":2026544,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"一言驚醒夢中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}